<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/kanishka-narayan> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Kanishka Narayan was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State in the Department for Science, Innovation and Technology on 7 September 2025. He was elected as the MP for Vale of Glamorgan in July 2024."@en .
